(205, '', '<p>This is a basic child of Product PATTERN. You see inherited settings, only Product description is overwritten.<br /><span style="background-color: #fcdb73; text-align: center; padding: 5px 40px;">Basically Manufacturer and Category are not inherited, for showcase reason both are set in this case.</span></p>', 'Advanced child', '', '', '', 'advanced-child'),
